title: Brunch de Salento
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Fast food, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Menu includes a veggie black-bean burger, a veggie burrito, and a few other vegetarian suitable items. Vegans to specify. Most products are organic and made in-house. Also sells fresh ground peanut butter. Has a cinema and Wi-Fi.
